text: Mitchell Thomas Duke (born 18 January 1991) is an Australian soccer player. He plays for Machida Zelvida in the J2 League and for the Australia men's national soccer team (nicknamed the "Socceroos"). ==References== Category:1991 births Category:Living people Category:Australian men's soccer players Category:Soccer players from Sydney Category:2022 FIFA World Cup players Category:Australia at the 2022 FIFA World Cup
